@database CompactwindowClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Compactwindow Class"


Compactwindow class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "WindowClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  CompactWindow class is used to create mini tiny windows.

  CompactWindow class is a subclass of CompactWindow.mcc, so you
  must have CompactWindow.mcc in MUI:Libs/MUI to use it.
  CompactWindow.mcc is copyright of Szymon Ulatowski.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}HVPreference@{fg text}
  N ISGN

  @{fg shine}NoGadgets@{fg text}
  B I

  @{fg shine}SizeGadget@{fg text}
  B I

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

@EndNode
